<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ yswʿ rby mnqdẖy ạlḥbyb ạ̉sknn qlby ạ̉nt ly ạlnṣyb
 ḥbk ạftdạny ṣrt fy slạm dmk ạsẖtrạny qd mḥạ ạlạ̉tẖạm
 ạlqrạr - yạ yswʿ rby mljạ̉y ạlʿẓym
 hb ḥyạty fyḍ rwḥk ạlḥkym
 qdsn qwạy rby ạlkrym
 wạrsẖdn kẖṭạy ṭrqk ạlqwym
 2- ạn bdạ̉ ṭryqy sẖạỷk ạlmsyr ạ̉w gẖdy̱ ṣdyqy mạkrạaⁿ kẖṭyr
 flykn slạmy wạḍḥ ạlwjwd fạlmsyḥ rby ḥạfẓ ạlʿhwd
 3- ʿṭfk ạlsẖhyr lạḥ llʿyạn ḥbk ạlwfyr bhjẗ ạlzmạn
 rwḥk ạlqdyr ḥl kạlsywl qwlk ạlmnyr yrsẖd ạlʿqwl</lyrics>
